```{r pancreas 32031712, include=FALSE}

PMID_32031712 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32031712', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32031712 <- paste0(PMID_32031712$journal,' ', PMID_32031712$year, ' ', PMID_32031712$month,';', PMID_32031712$volume,'(', PMID_32031712$number,'):', PMID_32031712$pages)

PubMed_32031712 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32031712$eprint)

doi_32031712 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32031712$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
